
            Video
            David Cameron: Brexit's 'less bad than we thought'
            Former Prime Minister David Cameron has been caught on camera at the World Economic Forum, in Davos, saying Brexit had "turned out less badly" than he expected.Mr Cameron, who quit as prime minister after losing the EU referendum in 2016, added "but it's still going to be difficult."
                
                        24 Jan 2018
                    
                
        
